data.description: WELCOME HOME to this gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 bath beauty with a 4 year old roof! As you walk through the front door, you'll be greeted by a stunning open floor plan with a spacious kitchen and large living room. The large owner's suite offers privacy & a beautiful bathroom complete with a garden tub! The guest bedrooms & bath are roomy. Enjoy the privacy & peacefulness the back porch & back yard offer, all while being minutes from restaurants, shopping, I-10 & more. Seller is offering a $5000 flooring credit with good offer.
